al"],"metadata":{"id":"HYDV8MC2reIf"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["-The model used all data for the training (black dots) and predicted the future stock price from mid 2018 to 2019\n","-It seems that the Google Stock Prices will be around 1400, based on the model prediction."],"metadata":{"id":"5SWmK3UzxI9I"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["m1.plot_components(forecast1);"],"metadata":{"id":"x2pUl_Rmri22","outputId":"b99e312d-4801-4461-c4d2-145a7a20df04","colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/","height":873}},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"image/png":"\n","text/plain":["<Figure size 648x864 with 4 Axes>"]},"metadata":{}}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["Based on the estimated trends, we can see that usually the stock price is maximum in the middle of june and mostly on wednesday. The trend plot shows an increase of the stock price in the near future."],"metadata":{"id":"5f2Kbm8RxtlM"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["#Adding the Holiday Effect\n","\n","ascensionday = pd.DataFrame({\n","  'holiday': 'AscensionDay',\n","  'ds': pd.to_datetime(['2015-05-14','2016-05-05','2017-05-25','2018-05-10','2019-05-30']),\n","  'lower_window': 0,\n","  'upper_window': 1,\n","})\n","christmas = pd.DataFrame({\n","  'holiday': 'Christmas',\n","  'ds': pd.to_datetime(['2015-12-25','2016-12-25','2017-12-25','2018-12-25','2019-12-25']),\n","  'lower_window': -1,\n","  'upper_window': 7,\n","})\n","new_holidays = pd.concat((ascensionday, christmas))\n","new_holidays.head()"],"metadata":{"id":"cTPbLHOSrqD8","outputId":"63ce21c7-15fe-4d9d-a1fd-27ae06016f56","colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/","height":204}},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"execute_result","data":{"text/html":["\n","  <div id=\"df-cb3e9aec-68c3-4ba6-baea-e89e7954549d\">\n","    <div class=\"colab-df-container\">\n","      <div>\n","<style scoped>\n","    .dataframe tbody tr th:only-of-type {\n","        vertical-align: middle;\n","    }\n",